Release Notes:

'My Maudlin Career' is the fourth studio album from Scottish
outfit Camera Obscura. Enlisting the help of producer
JariHaapalainen (The Concretes, Ed Harcourt) who produced
2006's 'Let's Get Out Of This Country', the album sees the
band continue with their unique Spectoresque indie-pop topped
off with Tracyanne Campbell's sweet Glaswegian vocals.
